claim.claim-text:
A capping machine (6) for applying caps (3) on respective open ends (11) of containers (2) made of a deformable material and filled with a pourable product, said machine (6) comprising:
- a conveying device (18);
- at least one operative unit (24) advanced by the conveying device (18) along a processing path (P) and in turn comprising support means (25) for receiving and retaining a container (2), and at least one capping head (27) movable to and away from the open end (11) of said container (2) to apply one said cap (3) onto the open end (11) itself;
characterized in that said operative unit (24) further comprises a plunger (40) movable to, and away from, one opposite closed end (10) of said container (2) to deform said closed end (10) inwardly of the container (2) so as to reduce inner volume of the container (2) itself and to increase its inner pressure.
